        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "ADAPTED BY JOSEPH JACOBS",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Once upon a time there lived a King who had seven Queens, but no children.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "This was a great grief to him, especially when he remembered that on his death there would be no heir to inherit the kingdom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Meanwhile the seven Queens lived luxuriously in a splendid palace, attended by hundreds of female slaves, and fed to their hearts' content on sweetmeats and confectionery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "The King, to allay their anxiety, promised regard for their wishes, and set out toward the south; but as luck would have it, although he hunted diligently, he found no game.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Nor had he more success to the east or west, so that, being a keen sportsman, and determined not to go home empty handed, he forgot all about his promise and turned to the north.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "However, when he would take no refusal, but implored her to have pity on him, promising her everything she could desire, she replied, \"Give me the eyes of your seven Queens, and then perhaps I may believe you mean what you say.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Now, very soon after the seven wretched hapless Queens had their eyes torn out, and were cast into prison, a baby was born to the youngest of the Queens.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "It was a handsome boy, but the other Queens were very jealous that the youngest among them should be so fortunate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "All these, things he brought home to his seven mothers, as he loved to call the seven blind Queens, who by his help lived on in their dungeon when all the world thought they had starved to death ages before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "At last, when he was quite a big lad, he one day took his bow and arrow, and went out to seek for game.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "At the first glance of the handsome young lad standing there bow in hand, she knew by witchcraft that it was the King's son.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "\"Poor souls!\" cried the cunning white witch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "\"Would you not like to bring them their eyes again?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Hearing this, the lad was delighted beyond measure, and gave up the pigeon at once.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Whereupon the white Queen told him to seek her mother without delay, and ask for the eyes which she wore as a necklace.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "So saying, she gave the lad a piece of broken potsherd, with these words inscribed on it, \"Kill the bearer at once, and sprinkle his blood like water!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "No sooner did the Princess catch sight of him than she blushed, and, turning to the King, said, \"Dear father, this is my choice!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Never were such rejoicings as these few words produced.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "When the beautiful bride heard his story, she asked to see the potsherd, for she was very learned and clever.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Ere long he arrived at the hovel in the ravine where the white witch's mother, a hideous old creature, grumbled dreadfully on reading the message, especially when the lad asked for the necklace of eyes. Nevertheless she took it off and gave it him, saying, \"There are only thirteen of 'em now, for I lost one last week.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "After this he set off to marry the Princess, as he had promised, but when passing by the white Queen's palace he saw some pigeons on the roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Drawing his bow, he shot one, and it came fluttering past the window.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "there was the King's son alive and well.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "She cried with hatred and disgust, but sending for the lad, asked him how he had returned so soon, and when she heard how he had brought home the thirteen eyes, and given them to the seven blind Queens, she could hardly restrain her rage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "The lad, nothing loth, gave her the pigeon; whereupon, as before, she bade him go and ask her mother for the cow, and gave him a potsherd where on was written, \"Kill this lad without fail, and sprinkle his blood like water!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "They were really frightful to behold, but, plucking up courage, he whistled a tune as he walked through them, looking neither to the right nor the left.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "The Jogi, seeing the lad, called out fiercely, \"What do you want here?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "One fell dead just beneath the window where the white Queen was sitting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Kill the lad, and sprinkle his blood like water!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "But when he looked in on his Princess, just to prevent her becoming anxious about him, she asked to see the potsherd as usual, and substituted another, on which was written, \"Yet again give this lad all he requires, for his blood shall be as your blood!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000044_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000044_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "He looked back, and lo!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Now as time passed by and the lad did not return, the old hag grew uneasy, remembering the message \"His blood shall be as your blood\"; so she set off to see what had happened.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "Now be off, before I repent of my kindness!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3142_160977_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3142/160977/3142_160977_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3142",
        "content": "So the son of seven Queens returned joyfully to his seven mothers, who, by the aid of the millionfold rice, soon became the richest people in the kingdom.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
